supabase/.temp
# Never ship a host-generated deno.lock into images. A host Deno can write a
# lockfile version the image's bundler/runtime Deno can't read, crashing the
# worker at boot ("Unsupported lockfile version N"). Deps resolve from deno.json
# (and functions are vendored into eszips), so the lock isn't needed in-image.
supabase/functions/deno.lock
